<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Special Invitation - Relable</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #dbeafe;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .benefits {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .benefit-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .benefit-icon {
            color: #059669;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="title">🎉 Special Invitation!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">{{InviterName}} invited you to Relable</p>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <h2 style="color: #2563eb; margin-top: 0;">🎁 Get 1 Month Free!</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                When you sign up and accept this invitation, <strong>you and {{InviterName}} will get 1 month free</strong> on any Relable plan!
            </p>
        </div>

        <p>Hello!</p>
        
        <p>{{InviterName}} invited you to discover <strong>Relable</strong>, the most advanced platform for reliability and degradation analysis.</p>

        <div class="benefits">
            <h3 style="color: #2563eb; margin-top: 0;">✨ What you get:</h3>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <span class="benefit-icon">✅</span>
                <span><strong>1 month free</strong> on any plan</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <span class="benefit-icon">🔬</span>
                <span>Access to <strong>LDA, RGA, DA</strong> analyses and much more</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <span class="benefit-icon">📊</span>
                <span>Professional reports and advanced charts</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <span class="benefit-icon">🚀</span>
                <span>Specialized technical support</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{InviteUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                🎯 Accept Invitation and Get 1 Month Free
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
            This invitation expires in 30 days. Don't miss this opportunity!
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 {{AppName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This email was sent by {{InviterName}} through the {{AppName}} invitation system.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 